1a9cb44e-bc30-4138-ac9f-59465df33380.13ff5f99-f709-4d52-9f3b-ca1bc0c37f71.description=
This operation does not do anything. It can be used to filter flow variables by defining them as inputs and filtering them in the Results tab.

Inputs\:
    invalidAccountFlag
    mismatchSurnameFlag
    repaymentTypeFlag
    incompleteDataFlag
    inDrawnDownFlag
    draftDateFlag
    dueDayFlag
    noDraftDateFlag 
    nextDraftDateFlag
    futureDraftDateFlag
    currentRepaymentFlag
    catchupPaymentFlag 
    draftAmountFlag
    incompleteDraftFlag
    redrawFlag
    draftBsbAccFlag
    draftBsbFlag
    draftAccountFlag
    cciPremiumFlag
    futureDatedFlag
    signaturesFlag
    branchStampFlag

These Are Reworks flags which will have the values True or False

Results\:
    rework - flag which will be set True or False
errorMessages - failure Message
Responses\:
    Success (Rework) – Proceed to Create Rework SLS Record
    Success (No Rework)– Proceed to Insert DDR Record into Automation DB

1a9cb44e-bc30-4138-ac9f-59465df33380.1bb7acb4-9174-4e78-8e39-034dd51e5cd3.description=
This flow will set the action date i.e update date for the DDR.
Transpose both PAYMENT FREQUENCY and FREQUENCY into it numerical representation using below table and transposed value for all calculation
Frequency	Numerical Value
WK, W1	1
BW, W2, SM	2
MO	3

Inputs\:
    paymentFrequency - frequency of the payment (WK,W1,BW,W2,SM,MO)
    frequency - frequency (WK,W1,BW,W2,SM,MO)
    repaymentDate - Repayment Date
    nextDraftDate - next draft date


Results\:
   actionByDate - calculated actionByDate
   futureDatedFlag - The possible values are True and False
errorMessages[List] - failure Messages


Responses\:
    Success – Proceed to Check For Rework Flags

1a9cb44e-bc30-4138-ac9f-59465df33380.7208f5e5-8b3e-4698-9b37-d7a0848b37c0.description=
Translate the output from DDR Form into a common input to create DDR Record

Inputs\:
    accountType - “SV” Type of the account
    paymentType - type of the payment
    mandatoryFields - this field determines whether document signed
    ddrType - type of the DDR
    CustomerLastName - last name of the customer
    loanNumberC - calculated loan Number
    requestedPaymentFrequencyC - calculated payment frequency
    requestedRepaymentOptionC - calculated Repayment option
    repaymentDay - day of the repayment (Ex\: Sunday, Monday...)
    preferredStartDay - preferred start day is in date format
    additionalAmountC - calculated additional amount
    draftAmountC - calculated draft amount
    draftAccountName - name of the account
    draftBSB - Draft BSB first 6 charectors of the account number
    accountNumber - account number of the customer
    draftFinancialInstitution - name of the Bank
    readFormFailFlag - if failed to read the email then set this flag True else False
    signaturesFlag - data recieved from DDRForm values will be True or False
    branchStampFlag - data recieved from DDRForm values will be True or False


Results\:
    accountType - “SV” Type of the account
    paymentType - type of the payment
    mandatoryFields - this field determines whether document signed
    ddrType - type of the DDR
    CustomerName - last name of the customer
    loanNumber - calculated loan Number
    paymentFrequency - calculated payment frequency
    requestedRepaymentOptionC - calculated Repayment option
    repaymentDay - day of the repayment (Ex\: Sunday, Monday...)
    preferredStartDay - preferred start day is in date format
    additionalAmount - calculated additional amount
    draftAmount - calculated draft amount
    draftAccountName - name of the account
    draftBSB - Draft BSB first 6 charectors of the account number
    accountNumber - account number of the customer
    draftFinancialInstitution - name of the Bank
    readFormFailFlag - if failed to read the email then set this flag True else False
    signaturesFlag - data recieved from DDRForm values will be True or False
    branchStampFlag - data recieved from DDRForm values will be True or False

Responses\:
    Success – Proceed to Validate New Application Number.
